Louis P. O’Connell, appellee, v. Stevens Hotel Company, appellant.Gen. No. 35,446.Heard in the first division of this court for the first district at the October term, 1931.

O’Connor, P. J., dissents.

Opinion filed February 29, 1932.Cassels, Potter & Bentley, for appellant; Ralph F. Potter and George C. Bunge, of counsel. W. F. McLaughlin, for appellee. Mr. Justice McSurely

delivered the opinion of the court.
